Package: lsmetacell
Title: Generate Library Size-Stabilized Meta-Cell Matrices
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Tianjiao", "Zhang", 
           email = "cb42277@um.edu.mo",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Tianjiao Zhang <cb42277@um.edu.mo>
Description: Tools for generating library size-stabilized meta-cell matrices from single-cell RNA-seq data. 
    This package implements methods to aggregate similar cells while accounting for sequencing depth variation, 
    reducing technical noise in downstream analysis.
